com.zhukovsd.generator

Enum MazeGraphKind

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<MazeGraphKind>
      • com.zhukovsd.generator.MazeGraphKind
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<MazeGraphKind>

    public enum MazeGraphKind
extends java.lang.Enum<MazeGraphKind>
    Enumeration of graph kinds, presented in maze generation process.

    • Enum Constant Summary

      Enum Constants 
      Enum Constant and Description
      DUAL_GRAPH
      Dual graph of initial graph, each its vertex corresponds to face of initial graph.
      INITIAL_GRAPH
      Graph with initial configuration of walls.
      PATH_SPANNING_TREE
      Spanning tree of dual graph, which represents all possible paths in initial graph.
      RESULTING_GRAPH
      Resulting walls configuration, which is initial graph non-including walls, intersected by path spanning tree.
      SHORTEST_PATH
      Shortest path in path spanning tree, which represents maze solution.
